<h2 class="bold font-l">The Weather- Spooky Fog</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Four snobby friends end up at a mansion and start speaking to the butler. Suddenly... </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Blackout Murder</span>, <span>Lights Out Somebody Dies</span> </h3>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
